description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home in the heart of South Boston’s vibrant South Boston neighborhood, ideal for homeowners and investors alike! Perfectly situated close to all the area’s best amenities, this property offers the ultimate in city living. The large living area is filled with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere, while the spacious kitchen features stainless steel appliances and plenty of cabinet space. Three generously sized bedrooms provide ample room for relaxation or a home office. The bathroom is well-maintained and thoughtfully designed. With restaurants, shops, parks, and public transportation just steps away, this home offers both convenience and comfort. To top it all off there is a 15 x 15 deeded storage unit in the basement. Just a stone's throw away from restaurants, bars, public transportation, activities, and coffee shops. Don't miss your chance to live or invest in one of Boston’s most sought-after neighborhoods!
